<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV101">
<l>iranturaippa tuṇṭuvāḻi yēmanīrti ṟattamā</l>
<l>varantarunti rukkuṟippil vaittatākiṉ maṉṉucīrp</l>
<l>parantacintai yoṉṟiniṉṟu niṉṉapāta paṅkayam</l>
<l>nirantaramni ṉaippatāka nīniṉaikka vēṇṭumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is something that [I] say making a request: May You prosper, O Lord</l>
<l rend="indent">whose nature is the joyful ocean’s!</l>
<l>If [You] have [it] in [Your] sacred mind to give an eternally superior boon,</l>
<l>[then] You should intend [my] wandering thoughts to remain focused on Your lotus feet</l>
<l>And think [of them] uninterruptedly!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
